s article is\npublished in two parts. The previous Part I has introduced the system and\nproved its completeness, while the present Part II is devoted to proving\nsoundness.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 29 Oct 2015 05:33:15 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 22 Jun 2016 12:21:10 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 1 Aug 2016 11:04:23 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Wed, 21 Sep 2016 13:46:11 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-03-14"}
