quivalence between a general class of partial\ndifferential and delay equation, modelling physiologically structured\npopulations.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 29 Oct 2015 10:15:22 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 31 Jan 2016 19:42:05 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-01-13"}
